      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a refined automotive selection that balances performance with enduring value. This vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard, showcasing a clean aesthetic and consistent mechanical integrity. It offers a sophisticated cabin environment and a smooth, confident driving profile. Rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our criteria for quality and safety, this offering represents an exceptional acquisition for those seeking a dependable and prestigious pre-owned vehicle.",
      "price": 32450.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
