      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec driver, powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. The power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. Technical integrity has been prioritized: the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the Vanos system has been professionally overhauled to ensure optimal cam timing. The suspension retains its sharp geometry with refreshed bushings, and the cooling system has been updated with an aluminum radiator. While the cosmetic condition reflects its use as a driver's tool, the mechanical vitals and chassis rigidity are excellent.",
